Create an API that acts as a store management tool
x- Create a Github profile if you don't have one
x- Use git in a verbose manner, push even if you wrote only one class
x- Create a Java, maven based project, Springboot for the web part
x- No front-end, you can focus on backend, no need to overcomplicate the structure
x- Implement basic functions, for example: add-product, find-product, change-price or others
x- Optional: Implement a basic authentication mechanism and role based endpoint access
- Design error mechanism and handling plus logging
x- Write unit tests, at least for one class
x- Use Java 9+ features
x- Add a small Readme to document the project
